description:
Ever wondered how to quickly find Squares & Cubes of Numbers between 1 to 100. Just in a few seconds each? This quick-fire method is the answer for that.

Total Video Tutorial of 60 Mins in 4 parts.

This course is designed for anyone and everyone who wants to make their life easier with MATH
title: Quick-fire Method of Squaring & Cubing of Numbers up to 100
